This is a placeholder for the architecture diagram PNG file. The actual diagram should be created using Excalidraw and saved as docs/architecture.png with the following structure:

[URL Stream] → [FastText Feature Extraction] → [Ensemble: XGBoost + LightGBM + RF + LR] → [Adjudication Layer] → [Risk Score + UI]

To create the proper PNG file:
1. Go to https://excalidraw.com
2. Create the diagram with 5 boxes connected by arrows as shown above
3. Export as PNG
4. Save to docs/architecture.png

The SVG version is available in docs/architecture.svg